API Documentation
Base URL
http://localhost:5000

Endpoints
Get All Bedrooms
URL: /bedrooms
Method: GET
Description: Retrieves all bedroom records from the "bedrooms" table in the PostgreSQL database.
Response:
Status Code: 200 OK
Body: A JSON array of objects, where each object represents a bedroom record.
Error Handling
500 Internal Server Error: Returned if there is an issue with the database connection or query execution.
Implementation Details
Database Configuration:
dbname: nostalgic_bedrooms
user: postgres
password: password
host: localhost
port: 5432
Logging: Configured to log INFO level messages to track the application's activities.
Running the Application
Start the Flask application with:
python3 api.py